categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A female Jedi Master lived sometime in the years between 800 and 200 BBY.

A Force-sensitive, woman was trained in the ways of the Force by the Jedi Order sometime circa 800 BBY. Attaining the rank of Jedi Master, she eventually came to possess a lightsaber uncovered on the abandoned world of Ossus. While she never revealed how she retrieved the ancient artifact, she passed it down to her Padawan before she trained her apprentice to Knighthood.
